            },
            {
              "chord": "D",
              "text": "你。"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "chorus"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "你何独行这条十架窄路？"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "前说恩言，今被人厌诅！"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "叹息声灭，欺凌却暴烈，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "神的爱子，何竟遭天绝！"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "2"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "我无法停止泪弹，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "当你忧伤回首看，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "想起曾说与你同苦难；"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "主，我的爱何等不堪。"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "chorus"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "你终独行这条十架窄路，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "各各他山，罪愆独背负。"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "钉痕的手，困我似囚牢？"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "无力脱开，枪扎的怀抱？"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "3"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "起初的爱未忘记，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "跟随的心却离弃，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "你爱我，竟为我舍性命；"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "主，我爱你却舍何情？"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "chorus"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "与你同行这条十架窄路，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "断绝世界，今生葬泥土。"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "\"你爱我吗？\"是的我爱你！"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "不再别依，随你脚踪起。"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "4"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "去罢！属地的贿赂！"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "去罢！虚假的祝福！"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "这条古老的十架窄路，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "主，爱你的人当同赴。"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "chorus"
    }
  ],
